          <node refid="T2" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>1016</offset>
        <text>This dampening, and the associated reduction in the intensity of predation, was accompanied by lagged increases in species abundances at both lower and higher trophic levels, first witnessed in zooplankton and then in large-bodied predators, all consistent with a return towards the earlier ecosystem structure.
</text>
